Category:Unidentified Sith of the One Sith

nodes.text: A member of Darth Krayt's New Sith Order, this Devaronian Sith was part of a group that attacked Emperor Roan Fel during the execution of Operation: Thunderstroke on the planet Agamar. He fought against Imperial Knight Azlyn Rae but was killed in the process.
